    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let go of the past\" sounds so easy to say but i don't want to let go of him. everything is just gray now. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. i'm just so tired of the weight of it all. it feels like there's no point to any of this anymore.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
