    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know if i want a brighter future. i just want to be where he is. it feels like we're on two different sides of a wall and i'm just stuck here on the wrong side. doesn't it seem weird that life just keeps pushing you forward even when you've lost the only thing that made it worth it?",
